edu.internet2.middleware.grouperClientExt.com.thoughtworks.xstream.mapper

Class AttributeMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.internet2.middleware.grouperClientExt.com.thoughtworks.xstream.mapper.MapperWrapper
      • edu.internet2.middleware.grouperClientExt.com.thoughtworks.xstream.mapper.AttributeMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Mapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EnumMapper

    public class AttributeMapper
extends MapperWrapper
    Mapper that allows the usage of attributes for fields and corresponding types or specified arbitrary types. It is responsible for the lookup of the SingleValueConverter for item types and attribute names.
    Since:
    1.2
